b'There are quite a few changes with Argentina\xe2\x80\x99s team. Scaloni has switched to a 4-4-2, with Lautaro Martinez and Paulo Dybala up front. Juan Cruz Oro comes in for Ocampos and Di Maria for Messi. Guido Rodriguez comes in for De Paul.'

b'Argentina play a 4-4-1-1, with Lautaro Martinez in front and Thiago Almada playing behind him. The midfield four consists of Ocampos, Paredes, De Paul and of course, Messi, while the back four is Tagliafico, Romero, Lisandro Martinez, and Montiel, with Emiliano Martinez in goal.'
